OL,3,CNorth Tyneside teacher retires after
OL,4,C47 years alongside pupils past and
OL,5,Cpresent
OL,7,FA North Tyneside teacher has held her
OL,8,Fretirement party today - after 47
OL,9,Fyears of working in the profession.
OL,11,FGlynis Bateman has worked at Rockliffe
OL,12,FFirst School in Whitley Bay since
OL,13,F1977. The pupils in the first class
OL,14,Fshe taught are now 50-years-old, and
OL,15,Fthey returned to the school to say
OL,16,Fgoodbye.
OL,18,FTeachers at the school have thrown Mrs
OL,19,FBateman a leaving do and invited every
OL,20,Fpupil she has ever taught to join them
OL,21,Ffor afternoon tea.
