OL,4,C47 years alongside pupils past and
OL,5,Cpresent
OL,7,FMrs Bateman told ITV Tyne Tees: "It's
OL,8,Fso exciting, so exciting. It's also a
OL,9,Flittle bit overwhelming and I just
OL,10,Fcan't believe I'm on the receiving end
OL,11,Fof something so lovely.
OL,13,F"I think sometimes you don't feel
OL,14,Fimportant enough to have something
OL,15,Flike this happen, but I work with such
OL,16,Fwonderful people that really it's no
OL,17,Fsurprise."
OL,19,FMrs Bateman emotionally thanks pupils
OL,20,Fpast and present for turning up to her
OL,21,Fleaving party.
