OL,7,FOne of Mrs Bateman's first pupils,
OL,8,FHelen, said she has "lovely, lifelong
OL,9,Fmemories" of her.
OL,11,FHelen told ITV Tyne Tees that the
OL,12,Fteacher was "very kind, very patient,
OL,13,Fever-present, but not imposing".
OL,15,FMrs Bateman taught Helen when she was
OL,16,Fin nursery, and then again when she
OL,17,Freturned to the school years later as
OL,18,Fa newly qualified teacher.
