OL,7,FShe said when she returned "knowing
OL,8,Fnothing" about teaching, Mrs Bateman
OL,9,Fhelped her find her way.
OL,11,F"I remember as an NQT she taught me
OL,12,Fhow to listen to the children, and I
OL,13,Fthink that's how my experience of her
OL,14,Fas a teacher must have been as well,"
OL,15,Fshe said.
