OL,3,CNorth Tyneside teacher retires after
OL,4,C47 years alongside pupils past and
OL,5,Cpresent
OL,7,FFellow school teacher Lindsay Ford
OL,8,Fsaid: "Mrs Bateman and I have worked
OL,9,Ftogether for nearly 30 years, and when
OL,10,FI got here she'd been already working
OL,11,Ffor 20 of those. And actually, I've
OL,12,Flearned so much from her, so much.
OL,14,F"She had so much experience, she could
OL,15,Fhave said 'do this, do that'. She was
OL,16,Famazing at letting me find my way. She
OL,17,Fwas so supportive, so welcoming. And I
OL,18,Fthink that's because she's always had
OL,19,Fthe children at the heart of
OL,20,Feverything she does."
